output.sentences: Our family decided to watch the parade in town today.
Some of my favorite characters were in the parade, like Spiderman and Captain Jack Sparrow.
Even Chewbacka from Star Wars was there!
There was also a guy dressed as Batman, but he wasn't very convincing.
At the end, these guys wearing airplanes looked like they were really enjoying themselves.
